  <h2>Facility Areas We Service</h2>

  <p>
    Comprehensive cleaning means addressing every area of your facility. We clean spaces ranging from executive offices to mechanical rooms, ensuring no area is overlooked.
  </p>

  <h3>Office and Administrative Areas</h3>
  <p>
    Private offices, open work areas, conference rooms, and reception areas receive thorough cleaning appropriate to their usage patterns. We clean around electronics and paperwork, dust thoroughly, and maintain professional presentation.
  </p>

  <h3>Restrooms and Locker Rooms</h3>
  <p>
    These spaces require detailed attention for hygiene and appearance. We clean and sanitize all fixtures, restock supplies, clean partitions and mirrors, and maintain floors. Deep cleaning includes grout cleaning, descaling, and fixture restoration.
  </p>

  <h3>Kitchens and Break Areas</h3>
  <p>
    Staff kitchens and breakrooms accumulate food spills and grime quickly. We clean countertops, tables, chairs, microwaves, refrigerators, sinks, and floors. Deep cleaning addresses appliance interiors, cabinet interiors, and behind equipment.
  </p>

  <h3>Entryways and Common Areas</h3>
  <p>
    First impressions matter. We maintain entryways, lobbies, hallways, and stairwells. Services include floor care, glass cleaning, dusting, and trash removal. Periodic deep cleaning addresses scuff marks, wall spots, and tracked-in soil.
  </p>

  <h2>Deep Cleaning Services Breakdown</h2>

  <p>
    Deep cleaning restores your facility beyond what daily maintenance can achieve. These services remove accumulated soil, restore appearance, and extend the life of your facility materials.
  </p>

  <h3>Carpet and Upholstery Care</h3>
  <p>
    Carpets act as filters, trapping soil, allergens, and contaminants. Regular vacuuming removes surface soil, but periodic extraction cleaning removes embedded dirt. Our <a href="/services/janitorial-services">comprehensive cleaning</a> includes hot water extraction that lifts deep soil, removes stains, and revitalizes carpet appearance. We also clean fabric office chairs and upholstered furniture.
  </p>

  <h3>Hard Floor Maintenance</h3>
  <p>
    Hard floors show wear patterns, scratches, and accumulated soil over time. We provide complete floor care including:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Deep scrubbing to remove embedded soil</li>
    <li>Stripping old wax and finish buildup</li>
    <li>Applying fresh coats of finish for protection and gloss</li>
    <li>Burnishing and polishing for ongoing maintenance</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Window and Glass Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Clean glass improves natural light and facility appearance. We clean interior and exterior glass including windows, glass doors, partitions, and mirrors. Services range from frequent interior cleaning to periodic exterior access cleaning.
  </p>

  <h3>Specialized Deep Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Some facility areas require specialized approaches. We clean high-ceiling dust, light fixtures, vents, HVAC intake areas, and other difficult-to-access surfaces. We also provide <a href="/services/construction-cleanup">post-construction cleaning</a>, move-in/move-out cleaning, and seasonal deep cleaning.
  </p>

